    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to an impeccable standard. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting flawless coachwork and an interior devoid of wear. Every component has been scrutinized to ensure mechanical perfection, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a meticulously preserved asset of the highest caliber.",
