      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive engineering, maintained in impeccable condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, exhibiting a level of preservation that is truly unrivaled. Every aspect of this motorcar\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments\u2014reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom quality. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering provides a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of distinguished pedigree and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
